OL,3,CRowers circumnavigating Britain in
OL,4,C'brutal' charity challenge arrive in
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FRowers enduring the "brutal" challenge
OL,8,Fof circumnavigating Britain to raise
OL,9,Fnearly #60 million for charity have
OL,10,Flanded in Scotland.
OL,12,FThe Row4MND team disembarked at the
OL,13,Fvillage of Port Logan in Dumfries and
OL,14,FGalloway at around 4.20am on Saturday
OL,15,Fafter rowing overnight from Northern
OL,16,FIreland.
OL,18,FThe four-strong crew are trying to
OL,19,Fraise #57 million to help find a cure
OL,20,Ffor motor neurone disease (MND).
OL,26,@oD@UOUoD@\O]
