OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773565532
OL,3,CRowers circumnavigating Britain in
OL,4,C'brutal' charity challenge arrive in
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FThe men have battled low temperatures,
OL,8,Fgales and heavy seas as they traverse
OL,9,Fthousands of miles round the British
OL,10,Fcoastline.
OL,12,FThey set off from South Wales last
OL,13,Fweekend but were forced to take a
OL,14,Fdetour to Northern Ireland, where they
OL,15,Fbecame stormbound.
OL,17,FFrom there, they rowed to the south-
OL,18,Fwest of Scotland and will soon take on
OL,19,Fthe rest of the nation's coast.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
