SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773565532
OL,3,CRowers circumnavigating Britain in
OL,4,C'brutal' charity challenge arrive in
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FRow4MND co-founder, business leader
OL,8,FMatt Parker, said the challenge is "a
OL,9,Fhell of a lot of hard work".
OL,11,FBut unlike those with MND, the Scot
OL,12,Fsaid he and his three friends could
OL,13,Fchoose to do the challenge, which they
OL,14,Fhope will help scientists find a cure
OL,15,Ffor the disease.
OL,26,@pD@dOUqD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
