OL,3,CRowers circumnavigating Britain in
OL,4,C'brutal' charity challenge arrive in
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,FMike Bates, fellow co-founder and an
OL,8,Fexperienced ocean rower, said the
OL,9,Fconditions have not always been good
OL,10,Fto the rowers.
OL,12,F"The weather wasn't on our side, but
OL,13,Fwe've still managed to cover an
OL,14,Fincredible 250 nautical miles over the
OL,15,Fpast week, and we spent some valuable
OL,16,Ftime gelling as a crew.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
