FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773565532
OL,3,CRowers circumnavigating Britain in
OL,4,C'brutal' charity challenge arrive in
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,F"We have achieved our objective of
OL,8,Fgetting to Scotland, with the added
OL,9,Fbonus that we also visited Northern
OL,10,FIreland: a true United Kingdom
OL,11,Fadventure.
OL,13,F"Our next, and arguably toughest, leg
OL,14,Fwill see us complete our
OL,15,Fcircumnavigation of Great Britain, by
OL,16,Ftraversing the rest of the Scottish
OL,17,Fcoastline, including the Western Isles.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
