PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1773565532
OL,3,CRowers circumnavigating Britain in
OL,4,C'brutal' charity challenge arrive in
OL,5,CScotland
OL,7,F"We'll be re-launching in early May to
OL,8,Fcomplete this challenge, having to
OL,9,Fcontend with vicious tides and
OL,10,Funpredictable seas."
OL,12,FOnce the crew has completed their
OL,13,Fcurrent challenge, they will focus on
OL,14,Fcrossing the Pacific ` from California
OL,15,Fto Hawaii ` in 2027, before attempting
OL,16,Fthe world record row between New York
OL,17,Fand London in 2028.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@TO]
